name: KOPI ALAS BALI
address: Jalan Bujak Penataran, Sepang Kelod, Kec. Busung Biu, Kabupaten Buleleng, Bali, Indonesia
review 1: Excellent coffee with nice service and peaceful atmosphere. You can also buy local ground coffee and Arak for good prices.
review 3: For coffee enthusiasm, you must try dark roasting from robusta. Coffee tree grow in the middle deep rain forest. That’s why they called “kopi alas” (forest coffee)
review 4:
The best coffee ever.
Pure robusta coffee
